OL,3,CFirst public war memorial devoted to
OL,4,Cservicemen in more than 100 years
OL,6,FThe first public war memorial devoted
OL,7,Fto servicemen for over a century has
OL,8,Fbeen dedicated in Ponthir this morning
OL,9,F(2 March).
OL,11,FNearly 100 people attended a ceremony
OL,12,Fthat was held to mark the occasion,
OL,13,Fincluding villagers from the Ponthir
OL,14,Fand Llanfrechfa areas and
OL,15,Frepresentatives from the Royal British
OL,16,FLegion and the Welsh Regiment.
OL,18,FThe commission follows an initiative
OL,19,Fby Ponthir Community Council for the
OL,20,Farea to have a public focal point for
OL,21,Fcommemoration.
