OL,3,CFirst public war memorial devoted to
OL,4,Cservicemen in more than 100 years
OL,6,FPonthir Community Council clerk Clare
OL,7,FDanaher hailed it a 'great success'.
OL,9,FShe said: "It's the first war memorial
OL,10,Fthat's been dedicated in our area for
OL,11,Fover 100 years so that makes it really
OL,12,Fimportant.
OL,14,F"It's a communal focal point and it's
OL,15,Fa monument to those who sacrificed
OL,16,Ftheir lives for us."
OL,18,FAn estimated 25% of the 70 local men
OL,19,Fwho served in the first and second
OL,20,FWorld Wars died, which is one of the
OL,21,Fhighest mortality rates in Wales.
