OL,3,CFirst public war memorial devoted to
OL,4,Cservicemen in more than 100 years
OL,6,FThe new memorial will play a key role
OL,7,Fin remembrance according to Clare.
OL,9,FShe added: "It will obviously be used
OL,10,Ffor remembrance day in November and
OL,11,Fthe school will maybe bring the pupils
OL,12,Fround to have a service and talk about
OL,13,Fthe war and how important remembering
OL,14,Four war dead is."
OL,16,FThe new memorial is a 24-inch square
OL,17,Fblock of dark grey polished granite
OL,18,Fset on a plinth in the Garden of
OL,19,FRemembrance at Zion Chapel by E. J.
OL,20,FHerbert of Newport who arranged the
OL,21,Fengraving.
