OL,3,CFirst public war memorial devoted to
OL,4,Cservicemen in more than 100 years
OL,6,FIt complements the Scroll of Honour
OL,7,Finside the Chapel listing the names of
OL,8,F25 young men who died in two world
OL,9,Fwars.
OL,11,FOn the wall nearby is a second list of
OL,12,Fthe 70 men who served.
OL,14,FThose remembered include Corporal
OL,15,FDavid Denbury, SAS Parachute Regt
OL,16,Fholder of the Queen's Gallantry Medal
OL,17,Fkilled in the Gulf War 21 Feb 1991
OL,18,Faged 26 and Albert Leonard Durnford.
